<title type="html"><![CDATA[NES Kung Fu Heroes Title Screen Rom Hack.]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=6057&amp;p=56692#p56692"><![CDATA[
Every game uses a different compression format. Some are straightforward run-length encoding, some involve horizontal strips of tiles placed at various positions, etc. If you want to hack a particular game, you may have to reverse-engineer the part of code that displays the title screen.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Tue Feb 16, 2010 5:15 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
